### MF Express Bot API Examples

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001
@botUrl = {{baseUrl}}

### Health Check
GET {{botUrl}}/healthz
Accept: application/json

###

### Bot Status
GET {{botUrl}}/status
Accept: application/json

###

### Register User in Chat
POST {{botUrl}}/register-user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chatId": "express_chat_123",
  "userId": "user_456",
  "username": "john_doe",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "metadata": {
    "registrationSource": "MultiFactor"
  }
}

###

### Send Authorization Request with Buttons
POST {{botUrl}}/send-auth-request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chatId": "express_chat_123",
  "userId": "user_456",
  "authRequestId": "auth_req_789",
  "message": "Попытка входа в систему",
  "resourceName": "Corporate Portal",
  "metadata": {
    "ipAddress": "192.168.1.100",
    "userAgent": "Mozilla/5.0...",
    "timestamp": "2024-01-15T14:30:00Z"
  }
}

###

### Send Simple Message (for testing)
POST {{botUrl}}/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chatId": "express_chat_123",
  "text": "Тестовое сообщение от бота",
  "type": 1,
  "metadata": {
    "messageType": "test"
  }
}

